SECTION 1 — REFUND POLICY
============================================================
Page 5

1.1 Standard Refunds
Refunds are allowed within 30 days of the original purchase date. The product
must be returned in its original condition and packaging. Refunds are processed
within 7 business days of receiving the returned item.

1.2 Digital Products
Digital products (software licences, e-books) are non-refundable once downloaded,
unless the product is defective or not as described.

1.3 Partial Refunds
Partial refunds may be issued at the company's discretion for products that are
returned in a used or damaged condition.

============================================================
SECTION 2 — WARRANTY POLICY
============================================================
Page 8

2.1 Hardware Warranty
All hardware products carry a 1-year limited warranty covering manufacturing defects.
The warranty does not cover accidental damage, water damage, or modifications.

2.2 Extended Warranty
Customers may purchase an extended warranty for an additional 2 years at 15% of
the product purchase price.

