SECTION 3 — PRIVACY POLICY
============================================================
Page 11

3.1 Data Collection
We collect personal data (name, email, purchase history) to fulfil orders and
improve our services. We do not sell customer data to third parties.

3.2 Data Retention
Customer data is retained for 7 years in compliance with financial regulations.
Customers may request deletion of their data by contacting privacy@acmecorp.com.

